# Component Folder Structure

- Each component must live in its own folder named after the component.
- Use `index.tsx` as the component entry file.
- Keep styles in a dedicated `styles.*` file in the same folder.
- Keep constants in `consts.*` files in the same folder.
- Keep helper logic in `utils.*` files in the same folder.
- Keep each file focused on one concern; avoid mixed responsibilities.
